<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 qīng zǎo shèng líng gǎn dòng wǒ jīn tiān yào chū fā dào nà yáo yuǎn de shān xià bǎ fú yīn zhǒng zi sā
 yīn wèi chūn fēng zhèng zài chuī chūn yǔ zhèng zài xià míng tiān zhǒng zi yī dìng huì fā yá
 zǒu a sā a zhǒng zi yī dìng fā xīn yá zǒu a sā a fā yá yī dìng huì kāi huā
 zǒu a sā a kāi huā yī dìng huì jié guǒ zhǔ de jiù ēn bì chuán biàn tiān xià
 tīng a tīng a gē zi de shào shēng chuán lái le kàn nǎ kàn nǎ fú yīn de duì wǔ qǐ lái le
 zǒu a chuán nǎ chuán nǎ zǒu a yé sū jī dū kuài huí lái le</lyrics>
